Package: hzd950-cups-driver
Version: @VER@
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: Run The Wall <hello@constly.com>
Depends: cups
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/RunTheWall/hzd950-cups-driver
Description: Free CUPS driver for HZD950-PRO / HERO TSPL thermal label printers
 A clean-room CUPS raster->TSPL driver for the HZD950-PRO (a.k.a. HERO Shipping
 Label Printer) 300dpi USB label engine, for Linux / Raspberry Pi and beyond.
 Builds from source, so it runs on any CPU the vendor's x86-only driver won't.
